UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='你不记得我了？该死的天灾军团……他们挫败了你的正义之气、泯灭了你最后一丝良知……还有你身为德莱尼人的天性！' WHERE entry=-1609043; /* content: You don\'t remember me, do you? Blasted Scourge... They\'ve tried to drain you of everything that made you a righteous force of reckoning. Every last ounce of good... Everything that made you a draenei! */
UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='你不记得我了？该死的天灾军团……他们挫败了你的正义之气、泯灭了你最后一丝良知……还有你身为侏儒的天性！' WHERE entry=-1609046; /* content: You don\'t remember me, do you? Blasted Scourge... They\'ve tried to drain you of everything that made you a pint-sized force of reckoning. Every last ounce of good... Everything that made you a gnome! */
UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='你不记得我了？该死的天灾军团……他们挫败了你的正义之气、泯灭了你最后一丝良知……还有你身为牛头人的天性！' WHERE entry=-1609050; /* content: You don\'t remember me, do you? Blasted Scourge... They\'ve tried to drain you of everything that made you a righteous force of reckoning. Every last ounce of good... Everything that made you a tauren! */
UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='听我说，$n。你必须对抗巫妖王的掌控。他是个恶魔，想要让这个世界——我们的世界——毁灭。别让他利用你实现自己的阴谋。你曾经是个英雄，现在也一定能不辱使命。战斗吧！结束他的掌控！' WHERE entry=-1609062; /* content: Listen to me, $N. You must fight against the Lich King\'s control. He is a monster that wants to see this world - our world - in ruin. Don\'t let him use you to accomplish his goals. You were once a hero and you can be again. Fight, damn you! Fight his control! */
UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='那里发生了什么事？怎么会这么久，$n？' WHERE entry=-1609066; /* content: What\'s going on in there? What\'s taking so long, $N? */
