UPDATE script_texts SET content_loc4='我会让你活着目睹这个末日，弗丁。这悲惨的世界将在我手中重铸，我不想让圣光最强大的勇士错过这一切。' WHERE entry=-1631162; /* content: I\'ll keep you alive to witness the end, Fordring. I would not want the Light\'s greatest champion to miss seeing this wretched world remade in my image. */
